title: Sabbath Bloody Sabbath
info:
SABBATH BLOODY SABBATH

by Black Sabbath
Tracked by Malekith for the Modules In Black music disk in tribute of
Black Sabbath.
Arranged and transcribed by Malekith in January and February 2000.
Guitar samples by Betrayer.


Actually I do not think this song is one of my best ones, since I had
difficulties to get this "70's feeling" into the mod. Yet I didn't notice
any big technical problem, here is the essential...
